  "release_notes": "Switches the Microsoft Store subscription Add-on Product ID from ChairsideReadyAlert.Subscription.Monthly to ChairsideReadyAlert.SubV2.Monthly. The original Add-on Product ID hit a persistent PEX-CatalogAvailabilityDataNotFound state in Microsoft's catalog backend (Add-on tile not surfacing on the parent app's Store listing, RequestPurchaseAsync returning the catalog error) that did not respond to any visibility, audience, or markets configuration we tried. Switching to a fresh Product ID lets the catalog establish a new association from a clean slate. No other code changes vs. v1.0.27.",
